'''Headhunters''' is an Indonesian team.

== History ==
'''Headhunters''' was founded by {{bl|Cruzher}} in October 2016 after he departed [[Revival Esports]] to found his own team to compete in the [[LoL Garuda Series/2017 Season/Spring Season|LGS 2017 Spring Season]].

